
Welcome to smarthouse project!

Contact author - kremvit@gmail.com


* Preparing:
  ========
# To prepare build environment run:
prepare.sh


* Building:
  ========
# To build smarthouse run:
make


* Running:
  ========
# To run smarthouse run:
bin/run.sh

# To run webclient developers server:
cd webclient
source virtualenv/kremvit/bin/activate
python manage.py runserver

* Cleaning:
  ========
# To clean smarthouse run:
make clean

# To clean environment run:
prepare.sh clean